title: SONGBIRD - The COVID Horror Movie No One Asked For | Explained
author: Think Story
comment:
It truly is a terrifying world when Alexandra Daddario becomes a camgirl.

The Worst TV/Films Playlist: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLY9KJ1cFVs7gkVDc9F4fvcy3Q1q_f5DKn
It's quite interesting how fast this movie was produced under the current conditions.
The fact that Michael Bay is a producer on this already serves as a red flag
Songbirds still sing even when caged, so they become a symbol of hope even in an inescapable situation. I assume they are the birds, CV23 is the cage, and their love is the song.
Imagine if announced they were making a 9/11 movie right after the towers fell.
